<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1918-11-03T07:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1918-11-03T07:00:00-05:00" n="861" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d861">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 763.72119/2744</note>
                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">The Special Agent at Corfu</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_DHP1" type="from"><hi rend="italic">Dodge</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                                </hi>
                            </head>
                            <opener>
                                <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Extract]</seg>
                            </opener>
                            <opener>
                                <dateline rendition="#right">
                                    <placeName>
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Corfu</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1918-11-03T14:00:00+02:00">
                                        <hi rend="italic">November 3, 1918, 2 p.m.</hi>
                                    </date>
                                    <lb/> [<hi rend="italic">Received November 4, 9.07
                                    p.m.</hi>]</dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>My October 16, 10 a.m.,<note n="1" xml:id="d861fn1">Not
                                    printed.</note> your October 2, noon,<note n="2" xml:id="d861fn2">
                                    <hi rend="italic">Ante</hi>, <ref target="#pg_334">p.
                                    334</ref>.</note> regarding Bulgarian armistice. A note just
                                received from Minister of Foreign Affairs states Servian Government
                                agrees with the Government of United States and has no intention of
                                asking for the settlement of Balkan questions before final treaty of
                                peace.</p>
                            <p rend="center">. . . . . . . . . . . . . .</p>
                            <closer>
                                <signed>
                                    <persName corresp="#p_DHP1">
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Dodge</hi>
                                    </persName>
                                </signed>
                            </closer>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>